{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·002.1", "text_original": "瞻彼中林，侯薪侯蒸。民今方殆，視天夢夢。\n既克有定，靡人弗勝。有皇上帝，伊誰云憎？", "text_normalized": "瞻彼中林，侯薪侯蒸。民今方殆，視天夢夢。\n既克有定，靡人弗勝。有皇上帝，伊誰云憎？", "notes": "正月 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·002.2", "text_original": "謂山蓋卑，為岡為陵。民之訛言，寧莫之懲！\n召彼故老，訊之占夢。具曰予聖，誰知烏之雌雄？", "text_normalized": "謂山蓋卑，為岡為陵。民之訛言，寧莫之懲！\n召彼故老，訊之占夢。具曰予聖，誰知烏之雌雄？", "notes": "正月 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·002.3", "text_original": "瞻彼阪田，有菀其特。天之扤我，如不我克。\n彼求我則，如不我得。執我仇仇，亦不我力。", "text_normalized": "瞻彼阪田，有菀其特。天之扤我，如不我克。\n彼求我則，如不我得。執我仇仇，亦不我力。", "notes": "正月 Chinese stanza 3."}
